These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: colombian, british, argentine, pakistani, australian, german, canadian
1. the british is in the middle##1
2. the british is on the left of the argentine##1
3. the australian is on the right of the pakistani##1
4. the colombian is on the right of the argentine##1
5. the canadian is on the far left##1
6. the german is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | canadian | pakistani | australian | british | argentine | colombian | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  photographer, accountant, paramedic, engineer, pilot, social-worker, fisherman
1. the fisherman is on the far right##1
2. the photographer is on the far left##1
3. the photographer is on the left of the pilot##1
4. the pilot is on the left of the paramedic##1
5. the engineer is on the right of the social-worker##1
6. the fisherman is on the right of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | photographer | pilot | paramedic | social-worker | engineer | accountant | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: collecting, reading, baking, photography, magic-tricks, filmmaking, singing
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | collecting | filmmaking | baking | singing | reading | photography |

 #################################

 
