.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-5::.
7 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, chinchilla, ferret, pony, fish, frog
1. the owner of the fish is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | frog | chinchilla | ferret | fish | cat | hamster | pony |

