.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: documentary, family, zombie, martial-arts, time-travel, musical, comedy
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | family | documentary | musical | martial-arts | comedy | zombie |

